sentences.english: Humans mostly see auroras in shades of yellowish-green.

sentences.english: I appreciate it mainly because of the deeply divided leaf lobes and the greenish yellow veins.

sentences.english: Later, they grow chartreuse fuzz , making pale green auras in the sun.

sentences.english: Look at the color of the grass–kelly green?

sentences.english: Well, my stomach hurts all the time, and my urine is greenish-yellow!
